 Time Chart）"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"传感器与执行器与节拍关系绑定","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmx16vjkts0","created":1782876669316,"text":"气路图","layout_right_offset":{"x":54.91666631204669,"y":653.3333145741523},"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmxj2iizug0","created":1782878070377,"text":"全局对象库挂载「标准气动回路模板」","layout_right_offset":{"x":3.410605131648481e-13,"y":-42.49999741050942}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djmxjjs2a6g0","created":1782878107959,"text":"执行器与标准回路绑定规则","layout_right_offset":{"x":4.999999695354177,"y":-44.16666397562767}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djmxk33vba80","created":1782878150031,"text":"利用AI批量拼接回路","layout_right_offset":{"x":13.333332520944168,"y":-39.99999756283239}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmx8351jfk0","created":1782877209732,"text":"AI审图","layout_right_offset":{"x":93.9999980078801,"y":-76.99999836815749}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmx835195k0","created":1782877209732,"text":"通用图纸检查"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmx83511h40","created":1782877209732,"text":"读取尺寸是否丢失链接报错、黄色悬空尺寸（图像算法）"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djmx8351jdk0","created":1782877209732,"text":"图框信息完整性检查（名称、图号、材料、比例、重量）（图像算法）"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djmx83515tc0","created":1782877209732,"text":"重量及尺寸信息单位正确性校验（重量KG，尺寸mm）（图像算法）"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmx835133c0","created":1782877209732,"text":"装配工程图评审"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmx8351en40","created":1782877209732,"text":"读取明细表，检查球标是否缺失、是否丢失链接关系（当前使用Design Checker）（图像算法）"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djmx8351f8o0","created":1782877209732,"text":"读取明细表，检查信息完整性（是否缺编号、名称或型号）（图像算法）"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmx835136w0","created":1782877209732,"text":"零件工程图评审"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmx83512vk0","created":1782877209732,"text":"检查漏注尺寸、漏注粗糙度、漏注技术要求（图像算法+数据分析）"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djmx8351cmg0","created":1782877209732,"text":"检查材料与表面处理匹配度（图像算法+数据分析）"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djmx8351jns0","created":1782877209732,"text":